SYNOPSIS
  lay <thing(s)>
  lay <thing(s)> aside|down
  lay aside|down <thing(s)> 

DESCRIPTION
  Recall an 'equipment'-declaration for one or more objects.
  The objects may be anywhere in your vicinity.
  Note that 'lay aside' does not mean that put actually drop the
  objects.

EXAMPLES
  lay torch aside

SEE ALSO
  equip, inventory, equipment
